OL,3,CBridgend mum starts online shop to
OL,4,Csell her daughter's second-hand clothes
OL,6,FA mother from South Wales has started
OL,7,Fan online enterprise to sell her
OL,8,Fchild's preloved clothing after buying
OL,9,Fsecond hand for years.
OL,11,FJulie Trott from, Llangeinor,
OL,12,FBridgend, who has always bought second
OL,13,Fhand clothing for her daughter Rae,
OL,14,Fhas taken the leap and started her
OL,15,Fonline endeavour 'Rae-cycle' after
OL,16,Fsporadically selling her daughters
OL,17,Fclothing online.
OL,19,FIn the midst of the climate crisis,
OL,20,Fshe hopes it will deter people from
OL,21,Ffast fashion options.
