OL,3,CBridgend mum starts online shop to
OL,4,Csell her daughter's second-hand clothes
OL,6,F"I've never done it for financial
OL,7,Fgain, but it's been such a godsend
OL,8,Fbeing able to buy second hand clothes
OL,9,Ffor her," she told ITV Wales.
OL,11,F"I want to encourage people to recycle
OL,12,Ftheir clothes because it's amazing...
OL,13,FI'm grateful to those people who were
OL,14,Fselling second hand because I was able
OL,15,Fto buy them for my daughter."
OL,17,FRae, who is on the neuro-developmental
OL,18,Fpathway, has reduced hours in school
OL,19,Fwhich means it is important for Julie
OL,20,Fto be available for her care.
