OL,6,FJulie formerly worked as an early
OL,7,Fyears practitioner, and now hopes that
OL,8,Fbeing self-employed will give her more
OL,9,Ffree time to look after her six-year-
OL,10,Fold daughter.
OL,12,FAccording to the Office for National
OL,13,FStatistics, the average cost of
OL,14,Fclothing went up by just under 2% to
OL,15,Fthe year leading up to June 2024 and
OL,16,F7.2% in the year before.
