OL,6,FJulie said: "In this day and age, it's
OL,7,Fmore cost effective (to buy second
OL,8,Fhand). Children grow so fast, and it
OL,9,Freduces the amount of waste that ends
OL,10,Fup in landfills.
OL,12,F"It reduces the need for clothing
OL,13,Fproduction."
