OL,6,FAccording to data collected by The
OL,7,FRound Up, an organisation that
OL,8,Fchampions sustainability and green
OL,9,Fliving, between 80 and 100 billion new
OL,10,Fclothing garments are produced
OL,11,Fglobally every year. In addition, 7%
OL,12,Fof the total amount of waste in global
OL,13,Flandfill space is made up of clothing
OL,14,Fand textiles.
OL,16,FJulie hopes her enterprise will see a
OL,17,Fchange in people's attitudes towards
OL,18,Fpurchasing preloved apparel.
