OL,3,CBridgend mum starts online shop to
OL,4,Csell her daughter's second-hand clothes
OL,6,F"Years ago, it was frowned upon to buy
OL,7,Fsecond hand clothes, but I always have
OL,8,Fand I'm trying to show people that
OL,9,Fit's okay.
OL,11,FJulie will be selling Rae's clothes on
OL,12,FEbay, which has the highest level of
OL,13,Fusage among UK second hand shoppers in
OL,14,F2024, according to the eCommerce
OL,15,Fdatabase.
OL,17,F"I'd rather brag about buying second
OL,18,Fhand clothes, at least I'm doing
OL,19,Fsomething that's helping."
